examples.en: She laughed to hide her nervousness.
The nervousness had dominion over me.
Mike's nervousness showed in his voice.
He hoped that his nervousness would go unnoticed.
You can feel the nervousness pulsing through the crowd.
The teacher imputed the student's failure to his nervousness.
Let's chalk up her weird behavior to simple nervousness.
A little nervousness is only to be expected when you are starting a new job.
The party had been overlaid with a certain nervousness.
Kenny wisecracked to hide his nervousness during the auditions.
